flowchart TD

A[Fellowship member detects danger] --> B{Send emergency alert?}

B -- Yes --> C[Alert is sent to the Fellowship]
B -- No --> D[No alert is sent]

C --> E[Location and situation are shared]
E --> F[Fellowship receives the alert]
F --> G{Can they respond in time?}

G -- Yes --> H[Help arrives]
H --> I[End: Situation is stabilized]

G -- No --> J[Help is delayed]
J --> K[End: Risk remains]

D --> L[User continues alone]
L --> M[End: Danger increases]
